{
  "title": "mac 下使用wireshark监听网络上的数据",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">分三个步骤：</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1.wireshark安装</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;wireshark运行需要mac上安装X11，mac 10.8的系统上默认是没有X11的。先去</span><a href=\"http://xquartz.macosforge.org/landing/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">http://xquartz.macosforge.org/landing/下载最新的</a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;xquartz安装，安装好就有X11了。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;wireshark的下载，网上有很多下载源。官网试了几次，没打开的成。可以考虑去华军之类的网站上下载。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2.打开网卡，允许wireshark访问</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;安装好xquartz和wireshark之后，需要打开网卡，允许wireshark访问。打开网卡的命令是 sudo chmod 777 /dev/bpf* 。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;每次开机后，执行一次就可以了。如果觉着执行这个命令还要输入自己的密码比较麻烦，可以考虑写个shell脚本，内容如下：</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$!/bin/bash</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;echo \"yourpassword\" | sudo -S chmod 777 /dev/bpf*</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3.启动wireshark,按需监控。</span>"
    }
  ]
}